Name: Saeg
Description: This rune symbolizes the bond between brothers and sisters, the bond of family and clan, and supporting those you care about. Those who channel this rune are able to bolster their allies, strengthening their courage and resolve.
Progression: Rune, Basic, Lesser, Greater, Epic
